7d116a65-55ee-4af8-8eae-9182301c8637.title: Mourner
7d116a65-55ee-4af8-8eae-9182301c8637.text:
I'm guarding the border to West Ardougne. No one
except we mourners can pass through.

880455ce-1a97-4316-b66d-497ead343629.title: Mourner
880455ce-1a97-4316-b66d-497ead343629.text:
The plague of course. We can't risk cross
contamination.

options.text: What brought the plague to Ardougne?
What are the symptoms of the plague?

76515b54-945a-4678-9d94-7f9a0ccf955c.title: <player>
76515b54-945a-4678-9d94-7f9a0ccf955c.text: What brought the plague to Ardougne?

a460f566-bc03-4272-be12-e735daf345e4.title: Mourner
a460f566-bc03-4272-be12-e735daf345e4.text:
It's all down to King Tyras of West Ardougne. It
started came back from one of his visits to the lands
west of here.

946190af-fb7a-44c6-b2e0-f0b9d6905d09.title: Mourner
946190af-fb7a-44c6-b2e0-f0b9d6905d09.text:
Some of his men must have unknowingly caught it out
there and brought it back with them

1d3bed2b-4fc4-420c-a997-b440d0940ab2.title: <player>
1d3bed2b-4fc4-420c-a997-b440d0940ab2.text: Does he know how bad the situation is now?

8a0d6caa-a8f9-47c5-b509-d000553706da.title: Mourner
8a0d6caa-a8f9-47c5-b509-d000553706da.text:
If he did he wouldn't care. I believe he wants his people
to suffer, he's an evil man.

165501f0-933b-474b-b6fb-140fffdb0c69.title: <player>
165501f0-933b-474b-b6fb-140fffdb0c69.text: What are the symptoms of the plague?

8efc12b2-1618-4e24-be7d-f076e16e85a2.title: Mourner
8efc12b2-1618-4e24-be7d-f076e16e85a2.text:
The first signs are typical flu symptoms. These tend to
be followed by severe nightmares, horrifying
hallucinations which drive many to madness.

d8d7f22c-853a-4687-99de-4b9fcbedfae5.title: Mourner
d8d7f22c-853a-4687-99de-4b9fcbedfae5.text:
It gets worse. Next the victim's blood changes into a
thick black tar-like liquid, at this point they're past help.

3b02c56f-a7a0-4d3e-998b-a6a95e3ceead.title: Mourner
3b02c56f-a7a0-4d3e-998b-a6a95e3ceead.text:
Their skin is cold to the touch, the victim is now brain
dead. Their body however lives on driven by the virus,
roaming like a zombie, spreading itself further wherever
possible.

3e0f1489-90ce-4dd1-93db-a16bc90ed8ce.title: <player>
3e0f1489-90ce-4dd1-93db-a16bc90ed8ce.text: What's the weird outfit in aid of?

0bc98152-9f80-4c82-aa2c-b8b9696bef74.title: Mourner
0bc98152-9f80-4c82-aa2c-b8b9696bef74.text:
All mourners wear this outfit. It's the only protection
from the plague.

dfe010a6-d59b-4885-9469-5594354f8a75.title: <player>
dfe010a6-d59b-4885-9469-5594354f8a75.text: I bet the ladies love it too.

d3cf6e27-d649-4ac7-b20c-ee570b2cf72d.title: Mourner
d3cf6e27-d649-4ac7-b20c-ee570b2cf72d.text:
This is no place for sight-seeing. Don't you know
there's been a plague outbreak?

8559b707-b5a0-401e-8e2a-34da797f2d76.title: Mourner
8559b707-b5a0-401e-8e2a-34da797f2d76.text: Then I suggest you leave as soon as you can.

options.text: What brought the plague to Ardougne?
What are the symptoms of the plague?

9e984fa4-1718-417f-b512-648f3f92919a.title: <player>
9e984fa4-1718-417f-b512-648f3f92919a.text: Sorry, what is it you do?

ce209863-de66-4270-bc69-5bd58af58b2b.title: Mourner
ce209863-de66-4270-bc69-5bd58af58b2b.text: I protect people like you from the plague.

6393b143-980d-41e9-9ceb-19fb09e903dc.title: Mourner
6393b143-980d-41e9-9ceb-19fb09e903dc.text: By making sure no one crosses the wall.

3143f527-2ead-4c0d-b454-fedba1d3d259.title: Mourner
3143f527-2ead-4c0d-b454-fedba1d3d259.text: Then they must be treated immediately.

acce84a8-f3ba-44c5-bc1e-2a70b479001f.title: Mourner
acce84a8-f3ba-44c5-bc1e-2a70b479001f.text:
Any West Ardougnians which cross the wall must be
detained and disposed of safely.

0700f4e1-e46b-4d54-ba23-859825d56b0e.title: Mourner
0700f4e1-e46b-4d54-ba23-859825d56b0e.text: Some find it hard, personally I quite enjoy it.

options.text: What brought the plague to Ardougne?
What are the symptoms of the plague?

855a432d-91fc-4605-8521-1e9a95123faf.title: Mourner
855a432d-91fc-4605-8521-1e9a95123faf.text: What? I'm pretty sure I haven't caught the plague yet.

0fdc563b-f492-4283-b6b6-37d94469a7b5.title: <player>
0fdc563b-f492-4283-b6b6-37d94469a7b5.text: How did you get into this line of work?

1d315a8e-ba75-4074-a7a3-63ad8381477f.title: Mourner
1d315a8e-ba75-4074-a7a3-63ad8381477f.text:
The mourners were recruited by King Lathas of East
Ardougne. It is our duty to protect his people.

e3e970bb-f719-44f5-b508-896ad517e742.title: <player>
e3e970bb-f719-44f5-b508-896ad517e742.text: I thought that was the job of the paladins and knights...

aa941d0b-3e14-49db-9c54-2b06bba775ac.title: Mourner
aa941d0b-3e14-49db-9c54-2b06bba775ac.text: Their swords and armour have no effect on the plague.

options.text: What brought the plague to Ardougne?
What are the symptoms of the plague?
Well, keep up the good work.

d7fb1f6b-3b75-41cf-b37b-1ae8f9ee062b.title: <player>
d7fb1f6b-3b75-41cf-b37b-1ae8f9ee062b.text: Well, keep up the good work.
